Three people were killed by unidentified persons this morning while at a food court in Garissa Town, motive still unknown. In Kiambu County police recovered four male bodies that were abandoned in a car in Gitaru area, off Nairobi-Naivasha highway. &nbsp;This comes in the wake of security concerns in different parts of the country. Baringo Country was recently declared insecure as leader called upon President Uhuru Kenyatta to take charge. &nbsp; ALSO READ: Bodies of four men found abandoned in Kikuyu